<br>
Also - a Gnomish Alliance - since Dwarvens are our brethren - distant kin, they too could be in it - that would not be an all-Gnome guild (which is what we try to accomplish).  And we are aligned with the HalfheightHeroes as is - cousins in a cousin guild ;-)<br>
